    <p>This online program was based on the European Vizamyl<sup
       class='trade-mark'>&trade;</sup> (Flutemetamol F18) Summary of Products
      Characteristics (SmPC). There are certain differences between the Swiss
      Package Insert (PI) and the European SmPC due to the national marketing
      authorization issued by Swissmedic.</p>

    <p>This electronic training contains important information to ensure
      accurate and reliable interpretation of PET imagines when using Vizamyl
      and serves as additional risk reduction measures to provide guidance to
      healthcare professionals. Side effects associated with the use of Vizamyl
      should be reported via electronic exchange to the Safety of Medicines
      Division, Risk Management Unit Swissmedic.</p>

    <p>Please review the Swiss Vizamyl PI on Swissmedicinfo before you continue.<br><a style="font-weight:normal;" href="http://www.swissmedicinfo.ch/" target="_blank">http://www.swissmedicinfo.ch</a></p>
